  <sect3 role="package">
    <title>Introduction to Quadrapassel</title>

    <para>
      <application>quadrapassel</application> comes from the 
      classic falling-block game, Tetris. 
      The goal of the game is to create complete horizontal 
      lines of blocks, which will disappear. 
    </para>

    &lfs76_checked;

